caption: Very beautiful church, which allows you to observe very beautiful colors. Particularly the stained glass windows, which offer splendid luminosity, and which are very original! This church is very pleasant, due to its dimensions, not too large, nor too small, but also due to the flowering of the latter. Multiple bouquets are sown in the four corners of the church. The fun little fact is that even the statues hold lilies in their hands! üòÅ
